summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of PoE 2 Passive Skill Tree Planner. All major functionality working correctly including canvas rendering with 2,552 nodes, professional game-accurate visual design, and full UI interaction capabilities.

Zoom controls work perfectly (zoom in, zoom out, reset view)
Class selector dropdown functions correctly (tested Witch to Ranger)
Level input field works (tested changing from 100 to 50)
Build name input field works (tested changing to 'Test PoE2 Build')
Search toggle button works (shows/hides search input)
Search input accepts text and filters nodes
Path mode toggle button functions correctly
Collapsible stat sections work (Attributes, Defensive, Offensive, Damage)
Expand All / Collapse All buttons work properly
Professional PoE 2 game-accurate visual design with cosmic dark background
Glow effects and thin connection lines working
Homepage loads at /en without errors
Navigation between homepage and build planner works seamlessly
Canvas displays 2,552 nodes with proper visual hierarchy
All interactive elements have proper data-testid attributes
No JavaScript errors detected
Responsive design and professional styling confirmed
